term & estimate & p\_value \\ 
\midrule
intercept & $-0.57$ & $0.31$ \\ 
Sepal.Length & $0.80$ & $0.00$ \\ 
Species: versicolor & $1.44$ & $0.04$ \\ 
Species: virginica & $2.02$ & $0.00$ \\ 
Sepal.Length:Speciesversicolor & $-0.48$ & $0.00$ \\ 
Sepal.Length:Speciesvirginica & $-0.57$ & $0.00$ \\ 
